Package CashItems

Class ItemCounterContainer

java.lang.Object
Monads.CounterContainer
CashItems.ItemCounterContainer
Direct Known Subclasses:
Sale
public class ItemCounterContainer extends CounterContainer
an array of ItemCounters this class is a CounterContainer that FORCES the types input into it to be ItemCounters as apposed to generic counters
